Transcription.Text: I feel certain that if one of my mantis survived others also survived along the mass of grape-vines, blackberries and other fruits and vegetables on my 1/8 acre. But if the one mantis I found in the autumn were the only survivor, the survival ratio was high, at around 1: 100.
